---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import imageStudent from '../../assets/images/student.webp'
import Container from '../Container.astro'
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden pb-24 sm:pb-32 lg:pb-0">
    <div class="absolute h-1/2 top-0 w-full bg-gray-50 -z-10"></div>
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 -z-10 h-[22rem] lg:h-1/2 w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-300 to-sky-600">
        <div class="w-full bg-uma-green-200 h-1.5 -translate-y-3 absolute"></div>
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-full bg-gray-50 h-1.5"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pattern -z-20"></div>
    <Container>
        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
            <div
                class="px-6 md:px-0 lg:bg-uma-green-400 lg:border-4 lg:border-uma-green-200 lg:px-8 lg:pb-8 lg:pr-4 lg:pt-10">
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-lg">
                    <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-900">
                        2024 Student of the Year
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="mt-2 text-pretty text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
                        Jada demonstrated academic excellence and peer support.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-sky-950">
                        Jada consistently demonstrated academic excellence,
                        tackling complex concepts with ease and producing
                        top-quality work. Her dedication to her studies was
                        reflected in her outstanding grades. Always focused and
                        engaged, Jadaâ€™s academic achievements made her a role
                        model for her peers.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-sky-950">
                        Jada was also a strong support system for her
                        classmates. She regularly offered help, whether tutoring
                        struggling peers or providing guidance on assignments.
                        Her generosity in sharing her knowledge fostered a
                        collaborative environment, allowing everyone to thrive
                        together.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
                <Image src={imageStudent} alt="UMA student" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>
